title: Ávila (Carlos Lôbo de)
body: This well-known statesman represented Madeira in the legislative session of 1890. He was born in 1863 and died on September 9, 1895.

Carlos Lôbo de Ávila: Statesman who represented Madeira in the legislative session of 1890.

1890: Representation of Madeira in the legislative session.
